  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Intra-operative NIRS measurements of kidney during partial nephrectomy, after reperfusion,&#xD;
      for monitoring ischemia and prediction of postoperative renal dysfunction.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
